xs font-medium text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark mb-2\">\n<span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]\">schedule</span> 5h 00m</span>\n<span>•</span>\n<span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]\">play_circle</span> 20 Lessons</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-text-secondary dark:text-gray-400 mb-2 line-clamp-2\">Advanced Bid Optimization</h3>\n<p class=\"text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary-dark text-sm mb-4 sm:mb-5 line-clamp-2\">Master the art of bid management, placement modifiers, and dayparting strategies.</p>\n<div class=\"mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-dashed border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary dark:text-gray-500 text-sm\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">info</span>\n<span>Prerequisite: PPC Fundamentals</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"group bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col h-full\">\n<div class=\"relative h-40 sm:h-48 w-full overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center\" data-alt=\"Group of people working together in a modern office environment\" style=\"background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAFKkfAsuT84uZ0zaeLW328uF0nPJlK9MXhXsEsNoVYJIt7BxvIvlNnweqsmbbgJW4-DtSyxIjQ-uM-NirCym9sDmh8XGbTK2myWYDFrb8N7FG49aD6DvAP6u-8od32e16KaEKeaz5UOaqfGAtyUbP47yg1mDgi6Gr705TULh-14UomZT0S6CAiDa8exk-4glHPmlki4RnHd2XiS9PymWx2kdYAvQrDMTBUH8h5uBruKpxc1bqDsFV4dxWIDL6En0M4Tq5XVJQpuG7u');\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-green-900/10\"></div> \n<div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/60 backdrop-blur px-2.5 py-1 rounded text-xs font-bold text-green-700 dark:text-green